"What is your mahatmaya? What is your importance?"

00:05:42.549 --> 00:05:46.424
He said, "My importance is, that when I'll come on this earth,

00:05:47.008 --> 00:05:50.549
when I'll rule on this earth, I know there will be bhranti,

00:05:50.758 --> 00:05:53.758
there will be chaos, there will be problems,

00:05:53.966 --> 00:05:57.591
but people will be so much fed up with that,

00:05:57.966 --> 00:06:00.716
that they will seek the truth.

00:06:01.091 --> 00:06:05.382
And those people today who are going to the hills and dales

00:06:05.591 --> 00:06:09.050
to find out the truth, will be there

00:06:10.133 --> 00:06:14.091
as ordinary human beings, as householders.

00:06:14.298 --> 00:06:17.298
