But we start feeling jealous and out of jealousy we start

00:07:42.883 --> 00:07:45.466
hating people without any rhyme and reason.

00:07:45.883 --> 00:07:48.091
So many countries have this problem.

00:07:48.424 --> 00:07:53.299
It's at the top, politicians,

