achievement of the other person is, how he has achieved,

00:08:06.133 --> 00:08:08.758
and "Why should I be jealous?"

00:08:10.925 --> 00:08:14.841
Then we have, another thing is apart from that is,

00:08:15.050 --> 00:08:19.008
which is the worst thing as Krishna has said, is the temper.

00:08:21.299 --> 00:08:24.508
Hot tempered people, you see, cannot see the truth,

