because at the slightest provocation

00:08:29.008 --> 00:08:33.091
they become hot-tempered and start hitting others

00:08:33.258 --> 00:08:36.633
and beating others or saying horrible things

00:08:36.883 --> 00:08:41.258
which should not be said. Now, this is another

00:08:41.674 --> 00:08:46.008
criteria for every Sahaja Yogi to know,

00:08:46.298 --> 00:08:53.716
how far he is out of this sense of "krodha", is the anger.

00:08:56.217 --> 00:09:00.050
To be angry it shows that you have

00:09:00.925 --> 00:09:06.466
no peace within and that you get angry for

00:09:07.133 --> 00:09:11.091
just to attack another person, which is not necessary.

00:09:11.466 --> 00:09:16.382
Even keeping quiet you can be very much effective.

00:09:18.008 --> 00:09:21.341
There's a story about Chinese people that

00:09:22.050 --> 00:09:25.050
in China there was a fight going on between

00:09:25.549 --> 00:09:31.382
some people, and they said, "Let's have the cocks fight for us".

00:09:31.800 --> 00:09:34.133
So they had a cock fight.

00:09:34.298 --> 00:09:39.008
So one fellow took a cock to a Zen fellow and he said that

00:09:39.298 --> 00:09:43.258
"What, what should I do, if this cock has to fight?"

00:09:45.050 --> 00:09:48.008
And he said that, "Very simple,

00:09:48.298 --> 00:09:51.008
you teach the cock to be absolutely quiet."

00:09:51.175 --> 00:09:54.133
He said, "I can't do that." He said, "All right, give me the cock."

00:09:54.298 --> 00:09:57.925
And he taught the cock how to be quiet,

00:09:58.298 --> 00:10:01.217
whatever is happening, whosoever is attacking him.

00:10:02.008 --> 00:10:06.633
When he went into the arena, many cocks started attacking him,

00:10:06.800 --> 00:10:10.258
and he was just standing quietly, watching at everyone.

00:10:11.091 --> 00:10:14.841
This settled the thing because everybody ran away and they thought

00:10:15.008 --> 00:10:17.591
he is such a powerful thing, he's not saying anything. So not

00:10:21.382 --> 00:10:25.382
attacking not reacting that we achieve anything.

00:10:26.175 --> 00:10:30.424
Actually reaction is a very great enemy of human beings,

00:10:30.716 --> 00:10:32.758
that we react to everything.

00:10:32.966 --> 00:10:36.466
We should not react, we should just become silent.

00:10:36.758 --> 00:10:40.091
And then this power, which I tell you about,

00:10:40.298 --> 00:10:44.341
is the power of Paramchaitanya, acts.

00:10:44.633 --> 00:10:47.841
If you want to react, all right. It says, "Go ahead".

00:10:48.175 --> 00:10:52.841
But if you leave it and you just become quiet,

00:10:53.217 --> 00:10:57.674
silent, it acts. It acts so well.

00:10:58.050 --> 00:11:02.591
It can act sitting down here, it can act somewhere else.

00:11:02.716 --> 00:11:08.091
It is such a tremendous power. It is such an effective power.

00:11:08.298 --> 00:11:12.008
It is such an understanding, knowledgeable power,

00:11:12.217 --> 00:11:16.091
and above all it loves, it loves you.

00:11:16.674 --> 00:11:21.091
So when this power comes into existence in a way,

00:11:21.298 --> 00:11:23.549
I would say it has been always existing,

00:11:23.716 --> 00:11:27.633
but when effective, in the Krita Yuga it is effective,

00:11:28.424 --> 00:11:32.466
by that you'll be amazed how things happen.

00:11:32.633 --> 00:11:35.800
Everybody tells Me, "Mother this miracle has taken place,

00:11:35.966 --> 00:11:38.133
that miracle has taken place. "

00:11:38.298 --> 00:11:41.341
So, I know it's not miracle. It is Paramchaitanya,

00:11:41.549 --> 00:11:44.925
which is doing all the work, all the beautiful things,

00:11:45.133 --> 00:11:49.091
which is trying to help you and trying to suggest its love.

00:11:49.591 --> 00:11:54.091
You see, it is something we can't see

00:11:55.050 --> 00:11:57.966
something we cannot conceive with this mind.

00:11:58.382 --> 00:12:02.050
But it is beyond the mind that it works.

00:12:02.298 --> 00:12:06.633
I was surprised in Russia specially, I had to face the scientists.

00:12:07.298 --> 00:12:12.217
Then the scientists were so, so much equipped, so much deep and

00:12:12.466 --> 00:12:16.298
they understood so well, even in a place,

00:12:20.716 --> 00:12:24.133
you can call it a place of great learning,

00:12:24.424 --> 00:12:28.091
one of the oldest universities, St. Petersburg University.

00:12:28.841 --> 00:12:32.883
There also I don't know, what made they gave Me

00:12:33.050 --> 00:12:38.008
the highest reward. For what? I didn't know.

00:12:38.298 --> 00:12:41.549
But they said, "You are even higher than science."

00:12:41.925 --> 00:12:44.508
So this they called as cognitive science.

00:12:44.841 --> 00:12:47.050
They gave a name as cognitive science.

00:12:47.298 --> 00:12:50.591
"So Mother Your whole knowledge is of cognitive science."

00:12:51.091 --> 00:12:55.674
Only thing is, if I tell you something then you can verify it.

00:12:56.133 --> 00:12:58.716
The scientists can verify it.

00:12:58.883 --> 00:13:02.674
Everybody can find it out if it so or not.

00:13:03.091 --> 00:13:06.883
