00:13:07.091 --> 00:13:11.175
you will see that they, they don't have any scientific basis.

00:13:12.549 --> 00:13:16.424
They have no way of giving you any explanation,

00:13:16.633 --> 00:13:20.091
as to why this is happening and what is happening?

00:13:20.800 --> 00:13:24.091
I had to face all of them all over the world.

00:13:24.298 --> 00:13:26.966
And I was surprised they recognized Me.

00:13:27.298 --> 00:13:31.633
And they said, "Mother this is cognitive science" and like that,

00:13:31.883 --> 00:13:35.341
they gave Me, everywhere they gave Me awards and things like that.

00:13:35.883 --> 00:13:38.633
I never knew what is cognitive science is.

00:13:38.800 --> 00:13:42.716
But this is the knowledge that you get beyond your mind.

00:13:43.298 --> 00:13:45.633
With your mind you get is your

00:13:45.966 --> 00:13:50.508
biased, maybe full of jealousy, maybe full of anger.

00:13:50.800 --> 00:13:55.298
But beyond the mind even you get this knowledge that is absolute.

00:13:56.175 --> 00:13:59.091
Nobody can challenge it, absolute knowledge.

00:13:59.633 --> 00:14:04.424
For example, I'll tell you one thing and if you see this model

00:14:05.382 --> 00:14:07.591
from the right side to the left side,

00:14:07.716 --> 00:14:10.008
there it will look like a swastika.

00:14:10.424 --> 00:14:13.050
I made a model for them, to show them.

00:14:13.508 --> 00:14:16.633
And if you see it from the left side on the right side

00:14:16.841 --> 00:14:19.008
it will be "aum" written down.

00:14:19.217 --> 00:14:21.883
And if you see from down upward,

00:14:22.298 --> 00:14:26.591
it is a cross, that means,

00:14:27.508 --> 00:14:32.800
Shri Ganesha, who is on Mooladhara, incarnates as Christ.

00:14:34.175 --> 00:14:36.591
So they made a picture, they made a model,

00:14:37.298 --> 00:14:39.758
the scientists, and they found out

00:14:40.341 --> 00:14:43.716
that what I said is true and this model

00:14:43.925 --> 00:14:47.925
really can be shown. I mean one of them is like this,

00:14:48.133 --> 00:14:51.633
that whatever you know, whatever you say,

00:14:51.925 --> 00:14:55.758
should be verified by even scientists.

00:14:56.591 --> 00:14:58.716
I do not discard science.

00:14:59.091 --> 00:15:01.966
Science is amoral, whatever you may say.

00:15:02.258 --> 00:15:05.549
But once they come to Sahaja Yoga, these scientists,

00:15:05.758 --> 00:15:07.841
they just get transformed.

00:15:08.133 --> 00:15:11.758
But scientists, in other countries, I don't know about our country,

00:15:12.050 --> 00:15:16.549
in other countries have reached such a state, such a state,

00:15:16.925 --> 00:15:20.716
that they want to know what is beyond.

00:15:20.966 --> 00:15:24.298
All of them come to India, why? Why don't they go to Japan?

00:15:24.466 --> 00:15:28.758
Why don't they go to China, why don't they go to America?

00:15:28.925 --> 00:15:31.716
To find the truth they come to India.

00:15:32.050 --> 00:15:36.549
So in India this cognitive science existed long time back,

00:15:36.758 --> 00:15:39.633
of which we are not aware.

00:15:40.341 --> 00:15:44.298
Like I must say, Indians suddenly became very westernized,

00:15:44.508 --> 00:15:48.674
after independence somehow, all Gandhiji's ideas,

00:15:48.883 --> 00:15:51.674
and everything was put on the shelves.

00:15:51.883 --> 00:15:55.424
So, we, we didn't know what was so great in our country.

00:15:55.758 --> 00:16:00.800
Such a great "sampada", such a great power

00:16:00.966 --> 00:16:05.800
existed in this country and they knew so many things,

00:16:06.298 --> 00:16:11.674
so many things about, some things that science do not know.

00:16:12.382 --> 00:16:15.258
Now it is for science to find out,

00:16:15.382 --> 00:16:17.925
whatever they have said it's true or not.

00:16:18.050 --> 00:16:20.633
I have seen this, it's very simple,

00:16:21.050 --> 00:16:24.674
if you really know the truth and you tell a scientist

00:16:24.883 --> 00:16:27.175
he'll get after it and he'll work it out.

00:16:27.925 --> 00:16:31.341
It's not one example, there can be hundreds I can give you,

00:16:31.508 --> 00:16:33.800
where I've told them something. They said, " All right."

00:16:33.925 --> 00:16:37.298
"You verify, you find out, by your scientific methods."

00:16:38.382 --> 00:16:42.758
And they found it, they found it. There's so many ways

00:16:43.091 --> 00:16:46.508
of finding it out, you have in science.

00:16:46.800 --> 00:16:49.133
But they don't know what to find.

00:16:49.382 --> 00:16:52.050
They are just going on in this one, that one.

00:16:52.217 --> 00:16:54.716
They are going to the moon, they are going to this thing.

00:16:54.883 --> 00:16:58.800
That's not the way. First you find out what you have to find

00:16:59.298 --> 00:17:02.091
and then see if it is there or not.

00:17:02.591 --> 00:17:05.591
I was surprised in the West, though we call them

00:17:05.758 --> 00:17:09.091
