about Indian culture and all that, they are so small,

00:17:38.298 --> 00:17:42.633
they are so incapable of

00:17:43.298 --> 00:17:46.716
telling them what it is. It has nothing to do

00:17:46.883 --> 00:17:50.382
with a fundamentalist idea, nothing of the kind.

00:17:50.633 --> 00:17:54.758
But it is a fact, it's the truth. it's the reality,

