He said, "Mother we are not". I said, "Why?"

00:19:04.299 --> 00:19:06.549
"Because we are in the kingdom of God,

00:19:06.716 --> 00:19:09.050
why should we worry about Russia?"

00:19:10.424 --> 00:19:13.716
You see, this also is a temperament that changes.

00:19:13.883 --> 00:19:15.883
and a person doesn't tell lies,

00:19:16.050 --> 00:19:18.966
but he really feels that way and that's how

00:19:19.175 --> 00:19:22.800
he gets rid of all these nonsensical ideas

00:19:23.050 --> 00:19:27.716
of religion, cast, nation, this, that.

00:19:28.716 --> 00:19:31.633
