With all these things they have helped us very much to show,

00:22:24.298 --> 00:22:29.508
that the essence of all these religions is one and out of that will

00:22:30.258 --> 00:22:34.883
one day people will take to Self Realization.

00:22:35.549 --> 00:22:40.424
