00:22:40.591 --> 00:22:43.341
Once they have grown into it, they can see.

00:22:43.508 --> 00:22:46.466
All of you know, you are all Sahaja Yogis sitting here,

00:22:46.674 --> 00:22:50.298
you know how much you have gained and how much you have achieved.

00:22:50.591 --> 00:22:53.800
So to give Me the credit, I don't know,

00:22:56.800 --> 00:23:00.758
it's not really true, because,

00:23:01.716 --> 00:23:04.091
we had great saints in some countries,

00:23:04.674 --> 00:23:07.382
great saints in this country, in every country,

00:23:07.716 --> 00:23:10.549
you know we had sufis in so many countries.

00:23:10.716 --> 00:23:15.091
They all have tried to say, that take your Self Realization.

00:23:15.549 --> 00:23:17.633
"Know thy Self."

00:23:17.966 --> 00:23:21.050
They all have said the same thing, "Know thy Self".

00:23:21.298 --> 00:23:24.298
But nobody is doing that, that's a different point.

00:23:24.549 --> 00:23:28.466
But actually all those who were Realized souls, whether they were

00:23:28.716 --> 00:23:32.591
from a Muslim religion or a Hindu religion or a Christian religion,

00:23:32.883 --> 00:23:37.382
any religion in any country if they were Realized souls,

00:23:37.800 --> 00:23:41.175
they said the same. Because truth is the same.

00:23:41.883 --> 00:23:45.633
They said the same thing, "First know thy Self"

00:23:46.298 --> 00:23:48.549
and then you will know the truth.

00:23:48.841 --> 00:23:52.883
So this is the essence of our life

00:23:53.091 --> 00:23:55.925
that we have to know ourselves.

00:23:56.050 --> 00:24:00.925
Once we know ourselves, you are beyond everything, because

00:24:01.175 --> 00:24:07.841
what happens that you become like an ocean becomes in this,

00:24:09.341 --> 00:24:11.883
like a drop becomes in the ocean.

00:24:12.091 --> 00:24:16.008
How it disappears... In the same thing it will happen.

00:24:16.341 --> 00:24:19.591
And once it happens, you'll be surprised,

00:24:19.800 --> 00:24:24.716
that you are really one with everyone. Who is the other?

00:24:26.258 --> 00:24:29.883
You are one with everyone, that's how we find in Sahaja Yoga.

00:24:30.091 --> 00:24:33.758
It's a, many people say, it's a big charisma

00:24:33.883 --> 00:24:36.424
it's big this thing. Nothing of the kind.

00:24:36.591 --> 00:24:39.382
You have your own Kundalini,

00:24:39.549 --> 00:24:43.758
you have own possibility, of becoming Self Realizing.

00:24:43.883 --> 00:24:47.716
Now, that is the blessing of Kali Yuga.

00:24:48.175 --> 00:24:50.298
In the Kali Yuga, this was going to happen

00:24:50.341 --> 00:24:52.008
and that's what it is happening.

00:24:52.175 --> 00:24:54.883
That's why thousands of you are getting Realization.

00:24:55.133 --> 00:24:57.591
Before, only one would get from one person,

00:24:57.758 --> 00:25:00.424
and those gurus were also very strict, you know, they

00:25:00.591 --> 00:25:03.298
would not give it to some ordinary person.

00:25:03.424 --> 00:25:08.258
They used to take them to task and judge them first.

00:25:08.382 --> 00:25:10.008
And then they would give Realization.

00:25:10.175 --> 00:25:12.758
But in Sahaja Yoga we don't do anything.

00:25:13.133 --> 00:25:16.133
You just have to get into Sahaja Yoga, that's all.

00:25:16.508 --> 00:25:19.424
Now, as it is, I'm surprised that

00:25:19.633 --> 00:25:23.549
how intellectuals and this and that try to find faults,

00:25:23.800 --> 00:25:26.841
without knowing that they don't know anything.

00:25:27.758 --> 00:25:30.633
They have to become Self-Realized people.

00:25:31.008 --> 00:25:34.758
Then, whatever they will do, that will be,

00:25:34.925 --> 00:25:38.298
definitely very constructive, very helpful,

00:25:38.758 --> 00:25:41.716
and peace giving, and harmony giving to the whole society.

00:25:42.633 --> 00:25:45.091
But first of all it has to be within you.

00:25:45.298 --> 00:25:48.298
If it is not within you, how can you give it to others.

00:25:48.925 --> 00:25:53.091
I've been watching how Sahaja Yoga has grown from one person

00:25:53.298 --> 00:25:54.966
to all these, so many of them.

00:25:55.133 --> 00:25:58.008
And we have so many others, in other countries also.

00:25:58.549 --> 00:26:02.966
This all has shown that the time has come

00:26:03.175 --> 00:26:05.549
for the whole world to change.

00:26:05.758 --> 00:26:10.758
And this transformation is the most important thing,

00:26:11.549 --> 00:26:13.341
what we should aim at.

00:26:13.508 --> 00:26:16.424
Forget about everything. Forget about politics, economics,

00:26:16.633 --> 00:26:20.008
this, that, but get transformation.

00:26:20.298 --> 00:26:24.424
Once you are transformed, you know how to do the right thing,

00:26:26.133 --> 00:26:28.298
how to do the things

00:26:28.424 --> 00:26:31.091
that will help you and the society.

00:26:31.883 --> 00:26:34.925
All these you already have seen in your life,

00:26:35.298 --> 00:26:40.008
and whatever is happened, is none of My only effort

00:26:40.217 --> 00:26:43.091
but there have been so many who have been doing this.

00:26:43.298 --> 00:26:47.341
Only if you can say anything is Me, is that I found out

00:26:47.549 --> 00:26:51.050
a way by which en masse Realization can be given.

00:26:51.841 --> 00:26:54.633
Many people can get it. Because any discovery,

00:26:54.800 --> 00:26:58.050
supposing there's electricity and if it cannot be used

00:26:58.298 --> 00:27:00.258
en masse, it is useless.

00:27:00.341 --> 00:27:04.591
So that's the only thing I've been able to achieve in My life,

00:27:04.758 --> 00:27:07.966
that en masse Realization can be given.

00:27:08.298 --> 00:27:12.341
And that has happen, as you know very well. It's very simple.

00:27:12.508 --> 00:27:15.758
And once one person gets Realization,

00:27:15.883 --> 00:27:18.008
he can go and give Realization to others.

