00:27:26.549 --> 00:27:28.841
Somebody went there and he did in that country,

00:27:29.008 --> 00:27:31.175
he went there, he did in other country.

00:27:31.298 --> 00:27:34.883
So, just imagine how simple it has become.

00:27:35.298 --> 00:27:38.758
How simple it is for Me. At this age I can't go

00:27:39.008 --> 00:27:41.091
to seventy, eighty countries,

00:27:41.298 --> 00:27:43.841
but it has passed there, it has gone there.

00:27:44.050 --> 00:27:48.133
